import React from 'react'
    import About from './About'
    import Home from './Home'
    import Nav from './Nav'
    import { BrowserRouter , Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
    

    function App (){

            return(
                <BrowserRouter>
                <Nav/>
                        <Routes>
                            <Route path="/Home" element = {<Home/>} />
                            <Route path="/about" element = {<About/>} />
                        </Routes>
                </BrowserRouter>

                

        );
    }



export default App
